data.description: Seller is offering $8000 in buyers closing costs!! Secluded home that sits on almost a half-acre lot in the city. Entire home has a new and modern feel. Tile and wood downstairs with brand new carpet upstairs (replaced 6/2023). Beautiful Kitchen has a gas range which is ideal for cooking. Exciting wet bar by the fireplace is perfect for entertaining. Beautiful bay windows for natural sunlight. Master down, all bedrooms and a huge game room upstairs. This is a must see.
